  "description": "A long, multi-span suspension bridge stretches across a body of water under a cloudy, overcast sky. A vibrant rainbow arcs over the bridge, originating and terminating beyond the frame of the image. The bridge appears to be made of steel and concrete, with supporting towers reaching upwards. The water below is choppy and grey, with some visible waves. In the distance, landmasses are visible, partially obscured by haze, and there are a few boats on the water. The lighting is soft and diffused due to the cloud cover.",
